---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
// swap to your real photo:
import WhyImg from "@/assets/tanktopandnico.jpg";
import Heading from "@/components/Heading";
---

<section id="why-use" class="bg-light-primary section-py">
  <div class="inner-section">
    <div class="twoCol-layout">
      <!-- Image (left on desktop) -->
      <div class="order-2 lg:order-1">
        <Image
          src={WhyImg}
          alt="Faria's team on the job"
          widths={[640, 768, 1024, 1280]}
          sizes="(min-width: 1024px) 640px, 100vw"
          loading="lazy"
          class="w-full h-auto object-cover"
        />
      </div>

      <!-- Copy (right on desktop) -->
      <div class="order-1 lg:order-2">
        <!-- eyebrow -->
        <Heading
          tagName="span"
          className="h5 font-semibold text-xl text-primary mb-2"
          >Why Choose Us</Heading
        >

        <!-- heading -->
        <Heading tagName="h2" className="text-dark-primary">
          Why Use Faria's Demolition And Disposal Services?
        </Heading>

        <!-- body -->
        <p class="mt-6 text-dark-secondary">
          Choosing Farias Demolition and Disposal for your demolition and junk
          removal services is choosing a partner who prioritizes your needs, the
          community, and the environment. With our years of expertise in the
          industry, we bring you professional, comprehensive, and safe
          demolition services, as well as responsible and sustainable junk
          removal solutions. Our dedicated team works relentlessly to ensure
          prompt and efficient service, while adhering to stringent safety
          protocols. In addition, we make it our mission to recycle as much as
          possible, actively contributing to a cleaner and greener future. At
          Farias Demolition and Disposal, we guarantee not just a service, but a
          commitment to excellence and responsibility in all we do.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
